Very talented and professional!
Nata took my brand photos, and I just can’t find words to describe how happy I am with the result.
I love each photo that Nata was able to capture, she was able to showcase my work perfectly!

originalText.text: I had a fun, easeful and professional experience when Nata photographed me.  Her demeanor is lovely, kind and skilful and she brings a sweetness to her work, which feels refreshing.  I was blown away by the photographs--how they so accurately portrayed my uniqueness and beauty in a natural and powerful way.  I highly recommend her for branding and any other photographs!!

originalText.text: We had the honor of having Nata Sokolovska document and photograph a masterclass in acting. She did such an amazing job. We ended up with almost too many options! She truly has a great eye. Very much exceeded our exceptions and what we need. I would highly recommend Nata!!

originalText.text: I really enjoyed this photoshoot with Nata that we took for my personal brand. We were shooting at my apartment studio over some tea, good laughs, catching the light of the day and the atmosphere was cosy and joyful which could bring such wonderful photos at the end. I'm grateful to Nata for capturing those moments, I felt myself more confident on making my first steps in the art world and positioning myself as an artist.

originalText.text:
My first business photoshoot in NYC was a nerve-wracking experience. I'm not a fan of taking pictures of myself, and I usually don't like how I look in them either. I'm sure many of you can relate, right? But working with Nata made everything so much easier. She helped me relax and made the whole process fun!
The best part came when I saw the final pictures. Wow! Nata really understood how to capture me through the camera. I was amazed by how she brought out the real me. She's not only a talented photographer but also a supportive and understanding person. I highly recommend her, and I'll definitely be going back to her in the future!
